* {{ a 1.5oz }} {{ i #gin }}
* {{ a 1/2oz }} {{ i #cointreau }}
* {{ a 1/2oz }} {{ i #creme-de-violette }}
* {{ a 1/2oz }} {{ i #lime-juice 'fresh lime juice' }}

Combine all ingredients in a cocktail shaker. Shake, and strain into a
Champagne flute.
